outputs.output_descr:
Expected Outcome:	
Losses related to socio-political, economic and environmental (including geological)crises reduced in the Arab States region through informed and proactive crisis response including political, diplomatic, economic and operational response, by the LAS.  

Expected Output(s):	
Analytical, early warning, coordination and operational capacities of the League of Arab States (SGLAS) enhanced to both anticipate potential crisis situations and to organize proactive, effective and timely crisis response, as and when required.

project_title: Strength. Crisis Response Cap. of League of Arab States
